<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.7.8">
<l>pakkaṅka ruñciṟuppā ṟaimītē yaruvikaṭ pakarntaṉaiya</l>
<l>vakkuvaṭa miḻintēṟit tāḻava ṇiyalkulpu ṭaipeyara</l>
<l>makkaḷula kiṉiṟpey taṟiyāma ṇikkuḻa viyuruviṉ</l>
<l>ṟakkamāma ṇivaṇṇaṉ vācutēvaṉ ṟaḷarnaṭai naṭavāṉō</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Just as rivers move upon the side of a small, dark hill,</l>
<l>as a string of bones hangs low, rising and falling,</l>
<l>[and] moves side[-to-side] on [his] ornamented waist,</l>
<l>[he] pours down [his grace] upon the human world,</l>
<l>unknown when [he] came to stay with the form of a jewel [like] child,</l>
<l>will Vāsudeva with complexion of a dark jewel come with a tottering walk?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
